data.description: Charming rural retreat! This spacious three-bedroom, two-bath manufactured home, with over 2300 sq. ft., is a perfect blend of comfort and updates. Built in 2003, it boasts newer flooring, a steel roof (2014), and an outdoor wood boiler (2017). Elevated on 16-inch piers, enjoy country living with an included 40x80 heated pole shed featuring a workshop and recreation room, a 30x40 three-sided shed for horses, pasture, riding arena, and an above-ground pool with a slide on a deck. Nestled on 60.61 acres, this property offers an outdoor enthusiast's paradise with hunting and ATV access at your doorstep.  These owners purchased with a VA loan. The house sits on (40) 16 inch Piers that are 8 feet deep. Easement to neighbor  cabin in back.  The outbuildings have 2 x 6 purlins in the roof structure, extra thick gauge of steel, hundred amp, electric, and water in the shop. The septic is a three tank at grade system. Approximately 30 acres are fenced.
